Package: bunddev
Title: Discover and Call bund.dev APIs
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Michael", "Bücker", , "michael.buecker@fh-muenster.de", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Author: Michael Bücker [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Michael Bücker <michael.buecker@fh-muenster.de>
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1.0)
Description: Provides a registry of APIs listed on bund.dev and a core OpenAPI
    client layer to explore specs and perform requests. Adapter helpers return
    tidy tibbles for supported APIs, with optional response caching and rate
    limiting guidance.
